3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper presents a polynomial time algorithm for the counting problem, which is a fundamental topic in algorithms and data structures. 
4. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - The paper discusses the complexity of the counting problem and presents a polynomial time algorithm, which is a key topic in computational complexity theory.
